@startuml Learnership Portal Complete Sequence Diagram
!define APPLICANT_COLOR #d8e8ff
!define PROVIDER_COLOR #d5f4e6
!define SYSTEM_COLOR #f5f5f5
!define ADMIN_COLOR #fef3cd

title Learnership Portal - Complete System Workflows

participant "Applicant" as APL APPLICANT_COLOR
participant "Provider" as PRV PROVIDER_COLOR
participant "System\n(Supabase)" as SYS SYSTEM_COLOR
participant "Admin" as ADM ADMIN_COLOR

== APPLICANT FLOW: Browse and Apply ==
APL -> APL: Sign in to platform
APL -> SYS: Request available listings
SYS -> APL: Return approved listings
APL -> APL: Browse available listings
APL -> APL: Select a listing
APL -> SYS: Check profile completeness\n(first_name, last_name, phone,\nlocation, date_of_birth, id_number, cv_url)

alt Profile incomplete
  SYS -> APL: Missing required fields
  APL -> SYS: Update profile
  SYS -> APL: Profile saved
else Profile complete
  SYS -> APL: Profile and CV ready ✓
  APL -> SYS: Click Apply (one-click)
  SYS -> SYS: Create application record\nstatus = 'Pending'
  SYS -> APL: Show confirmation message
end

== APPLICANT FLOW: Track Applications ==
APL -> SYS: View My Applications dashboard
SYS -> APL: Display all applications with status
APL -> APL: See current application status\n(Pending/Approved/Declined)

== APPLICANT FLOW: Notifications ==
note over SYS
  When provider updates application status
end note
SYS -> SYS: Create notification record
SYS -> APL: Send in-app notification
SYS -> SYS: Send email notification via Brevo
APL -> SYS: Mark notification as read
SYS -> APL: Notification updated

== APPLICANT FLOW: Favorites ==
APL -> APL: Browse listings
APL -> APL: Click favorite icon on listing
APL -> SYS: Toggle entry in favourites table
SYS -> SYS: Save/remove from favourites table
SYS -> APL: Favorite saved/removed
APL -> APL: View Favorites page
APL -> SYS: Request favorite listings
SYS -> APL: Display saved favorite listings

== PROVIDER FLOW: Profile Setup ==
PRV -> PRV: Sign in to platform
PRV -> PRV: Go to Profile Setup
PRV -> PRV: Fill profile form\n(organisation_name, phone, description)
PRV -> SYS: Submit provider profile
SYS -> SYS: Validate and save to provider_profiles table
SYS -> PRV: Profile saved successfully

== PROVIDER FLOW: Logo Upload ==
PRV -> PRV: Select logo image file
PRV -> SYS: Upload logo file (PNG, JPG, SVG)
alt Upload successful
  SYS -> SYS: Store file in provider_logos bucket
  SYS -> SYS: Get public URL from bucket
else Upload fails
  SYS -> SYS: Use base64 preview as fallback
end
SYS -> SYS: Save logo_url to provider_profiles
SYS -> PRV: Logo uploaded successfully
PRV -> PRV: Logo displayed on profile & listings

== PROVIDER FLOW: Filter Listings ==
PRV -> PRV: Open provider dashboard
PRV -> PRV: Select status filter\n(All/Pending/Approved/Declined)
PRV -> SYS: Query opportunities with filter
SYS -> PRV: Return filtered listings
PRV -> PRV: View filtered listings

== PROVIDER FLOW: View Applications ==
PRV -> PRV: Select a listing
PRV -> SYS: Request applications for listing
SYS -> PRV: Return list of applicants
PRV -> PRV: Select applicant from list

== PROVIDER FLOW: View Applicant CV ==
PRV -> SYS: Request CV (generate signed URL)
SYS -> SYS: Create signed URL to CV file
SYS -> PRV: Return CV link
PRV -> PRV: View/Download CV (PDF or DOCX)

== PROVIDER FLOW: Manage Application Status ==
PRV -> PRV: Review application details
PRV -> PRV: Click status dropdown
PRV -> SYS: Update application status\n(Approve/Decline/Remove)
SYS -> SYS: Update applications table
SYS -> SYS: Create notification for applicant
SYS -> PRV: Status updated
SYS -> APL: Send notification (in-app + email)

== ADMIN FLOW: Listing Moderation ==
ADM -> ADM: Sign in to admin panel
ADM -> SYS: Request pending listings
SYS -> ADM: Return pending listings queue
ADM -> ADM: Select pending listing
ADM -> ADM: Review listing details

alt Admin approves
  ADM -> SYS: Click Approve
  SYS -> SYS: Update opportunity status = 'Approved'\nCreate admin_actions log record
  SYS -> ADM: Listing approved
else Admin rejects
  ADM -> SYS: Click Delete
  SYS -> SYS: Mark opportunity as deleted\nCreate admin_actions log record
  SYS -> ADM: Listing deleted
end

== ADMIN FLOW: Export Reports ==
ADM -> ADM: Click export reports
ADM -> SYS: Request report data
SYS -> SYS: Generate CSV/PDF from admin_actions
SYS -> ADM: Download report file
ADM -> ADM: Save report locally

== ADMIN FLOW: Delete User Account ==
ADM -> ADM: Open user management panel
ADM -> ADM: Search for user by name/email
ADM -> ADM: Select user
ADM -> ADM: Enter reason for deletion
ADM -> SYS: Click Delete Account
SYS -> SYS: Cascade delete:\n- applicant_profiles or provider_profiles\n- applications\n- opportunities\n- notifications\n- auth.users
SYS -> SYS: Create admin_actions log record\n(account_deleted action)
SYS -> SYS: Invoke Brevo API\nto send deletion email
SYS -> SYS: Send email notification:\n"Your account has been deleted"
SYS -> ADM: User account deleted successfully

== END ==
note over APL,ADM
  Complete System Workflows
  All features integrated
end note

@enduml
